Best, 

John", "folder": "inbox", "read": true, "attachments": []}
{"type": "email", "id": "email_002", "subject": "RE: Vehicle Ownership Duration Analysis", "from": "emily.lee@elexionautomotive.com", "from_name": "Emily Lee", "to": ["john.davidson@elexionautomotive.com"], "cc": ["sarah.miller@elexionautomotive.com", "paul.watson@elexionautomotive.com"], "date": "2025-01-11 10:25:32", "body": "Hi John, 

