Best, 

Emily", "folder": "inbox", "read": true, "attachments": []}
{"type": "email", "id": "email_003", "subject": "RE: Vehicle Ownership Duration Analysis", "from": "paul.watson@elexionautomotive.com", "from_name": "Paul Watson", "to": ["emily.lee@elexionautomotive.com", "john.davidson@elexionautomotive.com"], "cc": ["sarah.miller@elexionautomotive.com"], "date": "2025-01-11 11:05:20", "body": "Hi Emily and John, 

